name: The As Yet Untitled Swirly Pipe Game
name_original: The As Yet Untitled Swirly Pipe Game
description:
This is "The as yet untitled swirly pipe game"

The object of the game is very simple. Tap the screen to move left and right, and don't hit the bars.

If you like this game, please do tell your friends, and don't forget to donate!

Thank you. :)
